data.description: 5 Acres, Doublewide and Singlewide home at back of property for mother-in-law or rental income. Acreage is 225 wide x 1,013 long. Width is road frontage, another small road down length of property. Property in county, no restriction on animals. Great horse country, goats, chicken, whatever!
data.whatILove: Kitchen and Dining room area, open and very nice layout. Large Master Bath with  garden tub, seperate shower, large walk-in closet. Both primary and secondary homes have plywood roof and floors.
